<div class="entry">
  <h3><a href="/articles/2010/08/08/heroku-radiant/">heroku + radiant</a></h3>
  <div class="posted">
      Posted by duggan on August 08, 2010<em>|</em> <a href="/articles/2010/08/08/heroku-radiant/#extended">Read full article</a>
  </div>
  <p>If you are thinking about using script/extension install whatever to install extensions on radiant you might want to think again. Heroku does not allow symlinks from github you have to wget the extension and place it in your vendor/extensions file manually.</p>


